Prerequisite
------------

Install these tools:

    - GNU Make
    - GNU C Compiler
    - raylib (optional)

Quick Start
-----------

Build labyrinthe with either:

    make && ./labyrinthe
    make GUI=1 && ./labyrinthe -g
